title: Champagne Cocktails by Lisa Shea
description:
Champagne cocktails are the perfect treat for every occasion, and this Champagne Cocktails book brings you 105 recipes for daily delight! Enjoy a green, minty bubbly while lounging in your back yard. 

Toast with a sapphire blue cocktail during your elegant evening. Party with bright orange mixers when celebrating with friends. A rainbow of colors and a cornucopia of flavors await you on each page.

Add in fun toasts, Champagne quotes, a step by step guide to opening a Champagne bottle, a wealth of photos, and you have the world of Champagne at your fingertips.

Genre: Non-Fiction, Cookery, Drinks
